ener">成为了 cHIP sHOP 和 Hennessey 庆祝 Hip-Hop 50 和英国黑人历史月的惊喜嘉宾</a>。</p><p>他还在今年 5 月的首届<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/goldie-ghetts-and-more-for-new-london-festival-project-6-from-outlook-organisers-3395794">Project 6 音乐节上</a>与<a href="/artists/goldie">Goldie</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/channel-tres">Channel Tres</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shy-fx">Shy FX</a>等乐队一起表演。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghetts-announces-new-album-on-purpose-with-purpose-conflict-of-interest-3515809">Ghetts 宣布新专辑《On Purpose, With Purpose》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
